OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1783765122
OL,3,CEngland World Cup winner Nobby Stiles
OL,4,Cdied with brain injury, court hears
OL,6,FFormer Manchester United player Nobby
OL,7,FStiles died with a traumatic brain
OL,8,Finjury, a court has heard as it was
OL,9,Fruled an inquest must be held into his
OL,10,Fdeath.
OL,12,FStiles, 78, who was part of England's
OL,13,F1966 World Cup winning squad, died
OL,14,Fwith chronic traumatic encephalopathy
OL,15,F(CTE), which has been associated with
OL,16,Fhead traumas and is claimed to be from
OL,17,Frepeatedly heading a football.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
