PN,36702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1783765122
OL,3,CEngland World Cup winner Nobby Stiles
OL,4,Cdied with brain injury, court hears
OL,6,FChris Morris, Area Coroner for Greater
OL,7,FManchester South, told Stockport
OL,8,FCoroner's Court that a brain expert
OL,9,Fhad examined samples and medical
OL,10,Frecords and - due to the injury - a
OL,11,Ffull inquest would be required.
OL,13,FNorbert "Nobby" Stiles died in October
OL,14,F2020 after a long illness, but his
OL,15,Ffamily has since campaigned for
OL,16,Ffootball associations to do more to
OL,17,Fsupport players with injuries they
OL,18,Fclaim were caused when they played
OL,19,Ffootball.
OL,26,@uD@IOUuD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
